    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a reliable ride with plenty of character! This well-loved vehicle is in fair condition, showing some honest wear from its time on the road, but it still has plenty of life left to offer. It's the perfect choice for someone looking for a dependable driver at a great value\u2014solid, functional, and ready for its next adventure!",
      "price": 22500.0,
